{"product_id":"norrskin-face-foam-cleanser-150ml","title":"NorrSkin Face Foam Cleanser 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNorrSkin Face Foam Cleanser won the Beauty Oscar for BEST CLEANSER IN SWEDEN 2022.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThis delicate foam will deeply clean you skin, leaving it softened, fresh and cooled down.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBenefits: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCleans your skin while boosting hydration level\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCalms down redness and irritation\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSupports regenerating and repairing processes in your skin with power of D-Panthenol and Linseed extract\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor All Skin Types, including sensitive, rosacea, eczema, and dry and oily skin.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLinseed Extract\u003c\/span\u003e is extra-rich, plant-derived source of Omega-3 fatty acids. Provides a nourishing and protective barrier for your skin, enhancing its natural glow.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNiacinamide\u003c\/span\u003e, also knows as Vitamin B3 and strong antioxidant, has a cleaning, detoxifying and brightening properties. Decreases redness and irritations on the skin. Stimulates elasticity.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eWild Strawberry Extract\u003c\/span\u003e is strong antioxidant. Contains amino acids, vitamins: B, E, K, PP as well as large amount of minerals, including Fe, P, Ca, S, K, I. It has cleaning, detoxifying and brightening properties.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e96,4% natural origin ingredients, dermatologically tested.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the foam on damp skin on your face and neck. Gently massage with circular movements. Rinse.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Betaine, Glycerin, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Lauroyl Sarcosinate, Niacinamide, Fragaria Vesca Fruit Extract, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate, Sodium Phytate, Parfum, Sodium Levulinate, Levulinic Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNatural Certified | Clean Certified | Vegan Certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eInspired by Hälsingland, Sweden.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNorrSkin plants 1 tree for every product sold.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"bioskina","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49308304834887,"sku":"","price":22.8,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/norrskin-face-foam-cleanser-150ml-479702.jpg?v=1739897337","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/norrskin-face-foam-cleanser-150ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}